    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for COU2 has been reviewed. Seven of thirteen credibility factors were assessed; all assessed factors achieved levels below required levels for MRL 5. Six factors remain not assessed. The Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification partially addresses input uncertainty. The overall assessment is accepted pending resolution of open items in the next review cycle.",
